<!--<h4>Text-1.</h4>-->

<p>
<lb n="1"/>svastiśrīmatu śrīnarasi
<lb n="2" break="no"/>ṁhadēvara (ra) raṁgamaṁḍpamu kaṁ
<lb n="3" break="no"/>(ṁ) bālu pāru<unclear>varu</unclear>
<lb n="4"/>varuṁbhani śrī<unclear>jī</unclear>yu
</p>

<!--<h4>Text-2.</h4>-->

<p>
<lb n="1"/>maḍuka palli nā
<lb n="2" break="no"/>yaṁḍu lakṣmīpa
<lb n="3" break="no"/>tiki cēyiṁcci
<lb n="4" break="no"/>na varuvu<unclear>ṁbha</unclear>
<lb n="5" break="no"/>ni
</p>

